output.analysis:
Let's analyze this post according to our criteria:
1. Has CMF: Yes - "CMF: 11240014" is present at the end of the post, indicating this is electoral propaganda material.
2. Refers to candidate: Yes - Directly mentions "George Simion președinte", who is one of the presidential candidates (Position 2).
3. Addresses wide population: Yes - The post is targeting a wide audience (100,001-500,000 people estimated reach), using paid promotion on Facebook and Instagram.
4. Electoral objective: Yes - The post clearly aims to influence voters by: - Promoting George Simion as president - Making campaign promises about agricultural policy - Using campaign hashtag "#AlbaVoteazaAUR" - Making political statements about sovereignty and EU relations
5. Journalism: No - This is clearly campaign material, not journalistic content.
6. Personal opinion: No - This is a paid, structured campaign message with CMF number.
The post contains classic elements of electoral propaganda: - Campaign promises - Direct candidate promotion - Political messaging - Call to action (implied through the hashtag) - Official CMF number

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This post clearly constitutes electoral propaganda because: 1. It contains an official CMF number 2. Directly promotes a presidential candidate 3. Makes campaign promises 4. Uses official party messaging 5. Is a paid advertisement targeting a large audience 6. Contains political program elements
conclusion.message-for-police: I AM ONLINE SRL, pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin promovarea unui mesaj de propaganda electorala dupa incheierea perioadei de campanie, difuzat după ora 18:00 pe 23.11.2024 prin intermediul unei reclame platite pe Facebook si Instagram (ID: 1693913901167510). Postarea promoveaza direct candidatura lui George Simion la presedintie ("Cu AUR la guvernare și George Simion președinte"), face promisiuni electorale specifice privind agricultura, contine numar CMF (11240014) si foloseste hashtag-ul de campanie "#AlbaVoteazaAUR", demonstrand astfel caracterul sau explicit de propaganda electorala pentru alegerile prezidentiale, cu intentia clara de a influenta votul in favoarea candidatului AUR.
